DESCRIPTION:This course is perfect if you’re curious about woodworking an
 d using tools.  You don’t need any previous experience to join— just c
 ome ready to learn and get ready to master some seriously cool skills! Wit
 h the guidance of experienced instructors\, you will use a variety of  dif
 ferent tools in our shop: the table saw\, band saw\, drills\, sanders\, ha
 nd tools and more.  SBWI instructors will ensure every student has one-on-
 one
